{"tid":2029323,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【雙層公寓】湖南美女龍夢柔取代Vivi　仲有「中國新垣結衣」之稱","createTime":"2020-05-22T07:39:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T05:05:04.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":71,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"63a55583a964452de7dbdd52b65f9ba379e18049","tid":2029323,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T07:39:40.000Z","msg":"日本真人騷《雙層公寓：東京2019-2020》雖然已經因為新冠肺炎（新型冠狀病毒、COVID-19）肆虐的關係而導致全面停工，不過在日本率先曝光的41至44集中，大受歡迎的俄羅斯模特兒Violetta Polt（Vivi）已經在第42集正式退租，今不少觀眾大失所望。<br />\n<br />\n「中國新垣結衣」<br />\n<br />\n不過隨着Vivi的離開，同時亦代表會有新成員頂替，而有「中國新垣結衣」之稱的龍夢柔就在42集緊接Vivi的離開正式入屋。24歲龍夢柔來自中國湖南，曾經在2014年參加《來吧！灰姑娘》並獲得冠軍，其後以栗子之名紅遍網絡。2018年，龍夢柔前往日本發展，還客串日劇《戀愛記憶》第7集扮演中學生。由於龍夢柔的樣子與「國民老婆」新垣結衣很相似，所以劇集出街後即引起網民大肆討論，紛紛讚她可愛。而龍夢柔在日本亦有出歌，亦曾經為雜誌拍攝水着靚相。"},{"pid":"206078abf3d2bd345145257b42d2e4f0682d10e9","tid":2029323,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":31,"score":-29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T07:39:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200521/340268299600400384.jpeg/-IJtCIuCsphkrRS1UusVJA3_zvgMS6BlCSOhXgkjoV4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200521%2F340268299600400384.jpeg%2F-IJtCIuCsphkrRS1UusVJA3_zvgMS6BlCSOhXgkjoV4&h=7ee56e4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n到日本發展時曾出過單曲《Planet》。（YouTube截圖）"},{"pid":"5266595c11e9a50241672a168d08dc6a80c281e9","tid":2029323,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":28,"score":-26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T07:40:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200521/340269843280433152.jpeg/fJnTDmvltz-tgft5gORGzI1mkZ89Xt2LqmtOvqprTr4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200521%2F340269843280433152.jpeg%2FfJnTDmvltz-tgft5gORGzI1mkZ89Xt2LqmtOvqprTr4&h=3f72ed71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200521/340269845436305408.jpeg/HpiAM736ZECfup4e4SHufNs0T8mUFbKvCDIp_wgyKf8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"htt